All the things are within the current folder
We only need all *File_XDATCAR_* files from the 2.
The file will be separated into 500 steps per file

##################################################################
You need to give the right path to the folder in both following files:
SUBMIT_JOBS_1.sh
remove_certain_files.sh

##################################################################
You need to modify several parameter in Hlist_proton.sh:
#How many protons are studied in the system
total_proton_num=`echo 2`

#Define the index num for the O at Surface, if your index has certain order, you cam create a loop
SO_St=`echo 33`
SO_En=`echo 64`
interger_SO=`echo 1`
##if your index doesn't have the order
#SurfaceO=(83,85,87,89,91,93,95,97,99,101,103,105,107,109,111,113)

#Define the index num for the O in water, if your index has certain order, you cam create a loop
WO_St=`echo 65`
WO_En=`echo 76`
interger_WO=`echo 1`
##if your index doesn't have the order
#WaterO=(115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126)

#The first index num of H
First_H_index=`echo 125`

##################################################################
Then running the following codes:
First:
./SUBMIT_JOBS_1.sh > LOG

Second:
./connected_all_reduced_or_Libby_finalOne_2.sh




